                                    Shortcuts
                                    ~~~~~~~~~
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
        F1   Shows the manual.
        F8   Renew the list of acronyms.
    control  F1   Runs the interactive help.
    control  W    Opens the Meaning webpage.
    control  Q    Quits Meaning.
